---
title: Chermoula Chicken Tacos with Quick-Pickled Onion & Herby Yoghurt
description: Few things look as colourful as these tacos – with the much loved chermoula-spiced chicken inside no less! The real star of this dish is
the dill and parsley-flecked mayo. There’s a herby hint amidst the expected creaminess of mayonnaise that works perfectly with each
element in tonight's dish and also means you’re in for a burst of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/quick-chermoula-chicken-tacos-7ea78fb4.jpg
